description:
The Pool of Bethesda is a special place to visit today for it is where Jesus healed a man who had been sick for 38 years. This is one of the most researched, well-visited and authentic sites in Jerusalem and where the question, 'Will you be made whole?', was posed. This is a question that resonates within our religious community today.
